Ekh '''korkori chhib''' si ekh [[chhib]] savya nai la pasharne, endaya chhiba, chi janel pes savya chhibatar avel. Kadya si le [[chhibavipnaske familiye]] saven si len numa ekh chhib, sar [[baskani chhib|baskani]], [[ainu chhib|ainu]], [[burushaski chhib|burushaski]], [[koreyanikani chhib|koreyanika]] thai aver.

==Le mule korkore chhiba==
Kana ekh purani muli chhib na janel pes mishto, phenel pes ke si korkori ji kana janel pes sar sas. Kadya si i [[Etruskani chhib|etruskani]], janel pes cira pe late, varesave manusha phenen ke si [[Indo-Europikane chhiba|Indo-Europikani]], ama nai dudalo. Si mule chhiba mishto jangle, sar i [[Sumerikani chhib|sumerikani]], ama si chache korkore chhiba, kana nai len aver pasharne, endaya chhiba.

